snippet.title: FreeSO Launch Trailer
snippet.description: After many years of crying, waiting, and crying more, we have finally made it to the end. Play The Sims Online in an all-new form: FreeSO. On January 6th, 2017, you can take part in the game reborn with features that work, jobs with friends, and creations with roommates. You can soon experience the game as it was and more improved.  It has been a long road, guys. We have finally made it to the end.
